  <tr><td>Obszidián Nyíl</td><td>+2</td><td>40%</td><td>—</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Réz Nyíl</td><td>+3</td><td>60%</td><td>—</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(192,192,128,0.10)"><td><strong>Ezüst Nyíl</strong></td><td>+3</td><td>60%</td><td>Extra sebzés élőholtak ellen + White Ghoul sebzésére képes</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Vas Nyíl</td><td>+4</td><td>70%</td><td>—</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(126,200,227,0.12)"><td><strong>Mithril-nyíl</strong></td><td>+7</td><td>80%</td><td>Legjobb sebzés!</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(179,136,255,0.14)"><td><strong><span class="wiki-item" data-id="adamantium_arrow">Adamantium-nyíl</span></strong></td><td>+6</td><td>90%</td><td>Az egyetlen nyíl, amely elpusztítja az End Kristályokat!</td></tr>
</table>
<table class="compare-table">
  <tr><th>Íj</th><th>Tartósság</th><th>Sebesség Bónusz</th><th>Megjegyzés</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Vanilla Íj</td><td>385</td><td>—</td><td>Standard</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(126,200,227,0.12)"><td><strong>Mithril Íj</strong></td><td>128 használat</td><td>+25% húzás és röpülési sebesség</td><td>Legjobbra fejleszthető (Legendary → Artifact)</td></tr>
</table>
<div class="info-box">🏹 <strong>Tegez / Nyíltegez (Quiver):</strong> 6 slot × 16 nyíl = <strong>96 nyíl</strong>. Kiegészítő slotba kerül. Receptje: 1 Toll + 2 Bőr.<br><strong>Legjobb kombó:</strong> Mithril Íj + Adamantium-nyíl — az End Kristályok ellen kötelező!</div>
</div>

<div data-lang="en">
<h2 id="armor-weapons-en">Armor &amp; Weapons</h2>

<h3>Armor Types</h3>
<p>Every metal tier has a full armor set (helmet, chestplate, leggings, boots) in both <strong>plate</strong> and <strong>chain</strong> variants.</p>

<h3>Set Bonuses</h3>
<table>
  <tr><th>Set</th><th>Bonus</th></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-copper">Bronze</span></td><td>+20% Sprint Speed</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-silver">Silver Copper</span></td><td>-10% Damage Taken</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-iron">High Carbon Steel</span></td><td>5% Damage Reduction per piece</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-mithril">Mithril (4/4)</span></td><td>+40% Sprint Speed, -30% Damage Reduction</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-ancient">Ancient Metal (4/4)</span></td><td>-30% Underground Damage, Vampire Bats won't attack, Corrosion Resistance</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-adamantium">Adamantium (4/4)</span></td><td>Immune to corrosion from gray/black slimes; fire damage does not reduce Durability</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Mercury Element (4/4)</td><td>Body temperature stays at 36.5°C permanently</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Armor Protection Values</h3>
<p>A total of 20 points = complete Protection. Armor loses its value below 50% Durability! <em>(Plate armor values)</em></p>
<table class="compare-table">
  <tr><th>Material</th><th>Helmet</th><th>Chest</th><th>Legs</th><th>Boots</th><th>Total</th></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-flint">Leather</span></td><td>0.42</td><td>0.67</td><td>0.58</td><td>0.33</td><td>2.00</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span style="color:#f0c040">Gold</span></td><td>1.25</td><td>2.00</td><td>1.75</td><td>1.00</td><td>6.00</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-copper">Copper / Silver</span></td><td>1.46</td><td>2.33</td><td>2.04</td><td>1.17</td><td>7.00</td></tr>
